qBittorrent Vanced — License
=============================

qBittorrent Vanced is a fork of qBittorrent Enhanced Edition, which is itself
a fork of qBittorrent. All original qBittorrent code is licensed under the
GNU General Public License, version 2 or (at your option) any later version
(GPLv2+). The binary distribution is licensed under GPLv3+ because it contains
GPLv3+ assets (e.g. images).

Vanced-specific modifications (theme, progress bars, UI streamlining, speed
controls) are released under the same GPLv2+ terms as the original codebase.

See the COPYING file for the full license text and OpenSSL linking exception.
See COPYING.GPLv2 for the GPLv2 license text.
See COPYING.GPLv3 for the GPLv3 license text.

